OUR SERVICES

Making the world a smaller place

  • DELHIVERY EXPRESS
  • DELHIVERY FULFILMENT
  • DELHIVERY FREIGHT
  • DELHIVERY CROSS-BORDER
  • DELHIVERY E2E

DELHIVERY FULFILMENT

We operate over 71 fulfilment centers across India, with over 6 million sq ft of storage and processing space. Our proprietary warehouse management system is integrated with all the major demand channels and courier partners. It is designed to enable efficient multi-tenant, multi-location warehousing – allowing clients to quickly and flexibly scale operations across India with zero fixed costs. We also offer integrated distribution solutions to enterprises by combining our warehousing and freight solutions. This facilitates fast and cost-efficient offline distribution.

FULFILMENT SERVICES

Multi-channel B2C Order Fulfilment

B2B Order Fulfilment

Returns Management

Courier Selection and Management

Category-specific Fulfilment(Furniture/White Goods)

TECHNOLOGY SERVICES

Distributed Order Management

Global Inventory Visibility and Management

Channel Integration and Management

Courier Selection and Management

Contact Us
